entries.title_d: Deliver the crystals to a command shuttle in the Dathomir system. Whatever those crystals are, those mercenaries want them back badly.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Deliver the Crystals
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the arrival location and wait for the shuttle.
entries.quest_location_d: The shuttle will meet you in the Dathomir system.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the shuttle and transfer the crystals to it.
entries.hello_d: Hello, pilot. I am here to pick up some cargo you pulled off of a smuggler. Your commander wants to speak with you after this.
entries.found_loc_d: Transport shuttle will meet you at the location supplied in your nav computer.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Cargo has been transfered to the transport shuttle.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by for arrival of the transport shuttle.
